{"tid":2225083,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SM人氣女練習生被曝說「EXO KAI好醜」","createTime":"2020-10-01T04:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T00:47:36.000Z","uid":74065,"like":98,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"1b83d4b8ecc6f6d9a8f712d25bed42d4c5974cf8","tid":2225083,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/09/30/550_1546638_1601402785.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F09%2F30%2F550_1546638_1601402785.webp&h=96bb2122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日，據韓媒報導，SM娛樂公司旗下女練習生疑因在背後議論男子組合EXO成員KAI而引起了爭議。<br />\n<br />\n29日，在韓國某網絡討論區中，有網民上傳了題目為「SM練習生劉智敏在背後說EXO成員KAI閒話」的帖子。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/09/30/550_1546637_1601402781.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F09%2F30%2F550_1546637_1601402781.webp&h=b7c8000f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據悉，劉智敏（音）是SM現役00年生女子練習生，曾出演泰民的《WANT》MV，是在粉絲圈中擁有很高知名度的練習生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/09/30/550_1546636_1601402773.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F09%2F30%2F550_1546636_1601402773.webp&h=0d524842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從網民公開的第一張照片來看，被推測是劉智敏的Instagram賬號中上傳了一句句子--「南楊州拍攝現在開始， ㅋㅇ，醜」（ㅋㅇ為KAI韓語카이的初聲）的帖子，網民表示，劉智敏應該是跟KAI一起拍攝了關於車的廣告。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/09/30/550_1546635_1601402769.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F09%2F30%2F550_1546635_1601402769.webp&h=d817e428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n接着，在另一張圖片中，疑似是劉智敏和朋友的手機對話截圖，她說：「今天和EXO的KAI一起進行了拍攝，在南楊州，哈哈哈」又說：「哈哈哈，真的一般般」及「還不如和EXO其他成員一起拍呢，哼」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/09/30/550_1546640_1601402794.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F09%2F30%2F550_1546640_1601402794.webp&h=9a3e0eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/09/30/550_1546639_1601402790.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F09%2F30%2F550_1546639_1601402790.webp&h=56893415&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n看到此帖文後，部分的EXO粉絲們都對作為KAI後輩的劉智敏的輕率發言感到憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n網民們紛紛表示：「KAI有什麼罪啊...」、「她雖然也做錯了，但她朋友竟然馬上截圖上傳」、「別出道了吧」。大家又怎麼看呢？"},{"pid":"0bb8a8d36e3161a1102af9b471808d8fff949eab","tid":2225083,"uid":143093,"like":113,"dislike":9,"score":104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:55:22.000Z","msg":"條女仲7"},{"pid":"1210c5ef5541e68400c98908029a1cb76b8945d9","tid":2225083,"uid":40470,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:57:33.000Z","msg":"大陸非主流民工"},{"pid":"e5b9cbdaa9f0668932fad38ea97fda015d9ddd36","tid":2225083,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"肉酸"},{"pid":"5994a867e592fed817d26de8d56455245b5a59b0","tid":2225083,"uid":256952,"like":111,"dislike":4,"score":107,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:47:39.000Z","msg":"唔洗旨意出道 就算出左都會diss死她"},{"pid":"0884bc1f649dc040de938565e95ca071e202b901","tid":2225083,"uid":68678,"like":228,"dislike":7,"score":221,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:48:43.000Z","msg":"講事實都唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9d1de1770581c4cfb2f17e477d19e401900a1d","tid":2225083,"uid":87988,"like":367,"dislike":10,"score":357,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"咁KAI真係醜wor..."},{"pid":"e9dfe4a0dc29df1de8ffbc8c72bc469d2b64cf80","tid":2225083,"uid":555,"like":64,"dislike":4,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:51:08.000Z","msg":"咁係醜嘛"},{"pid":"de48b8866d704c19f334f614da4a7f03104becf9","tid":2225083,"uid":141462,"like":77,"dislike":5,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:55:41.000Z","msg":"事實喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5025341d5a4a06f2454bc232f9606f059f7906","tid":2225083,"u